{
  "cleanUrls": true,
  "rewrites": [
    { "source": "/(.*)", "destination": "/index.html" }
  ]
}
```

The `cleanUrls: true` tells Vercel to serve `login.html` when someone visits `/login`, `terms.html` for `/terms`, etc. automatically.

Then update your footer links in `index.html` — change:
```
href="/privacy.html"  →  href="/privacy"
href="/terms.html"    →  href="/terms"
href="/login.html"    →  href="/login"
```

And in `login.html` change:
```
href="/terms.html"    →  href="/terms"
href="/privacy.html"  →  href="/privacy"
